shortDescription: Satellite recon shows a company of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} military units is engaged in a search and destroy mission on planet. They are still far enough from Tweak's location that our friends aren't in immediate danger, but we must eliminate these forces before we can make any attempt at an extraction.
longDescription: This is a straightforward battle, Commander. It's nothing we haven't handled before. Just more targets.

dialogueContent.words: We've got them, Commander. They're moving alongside the highway. But there are a lot more units than we expected.
Our first target is designed Strike Lance Alpha. Additional targets will be designated as we get a good fix on them.
We have a comm signal from Tweak, Commander. I'm putting her through.
Commander {COMMANDER.LastName}, my people are surrounded. I'm afraid that by the time this reaches you, our position will be overrun. Please, if you can, hurry.
You heard the lady. I'm coming in hot, Commander. Let's see if we can't get you over there before its too late.
This isn't going to work, Commander. We will need to figure out another way to go about getting help to Tweak.
Stow it. We don't need to hear about friendlies down.
Shut up about the friendly units dying.
All our stupid allies are finally dead.
Darius, we have a fix on those additional units. It's another DEST squad.
Unknown mercenary force, you are intruding on a Kuritan operation. Withdraw or you will be destroyed.
Commander, we'll need to engage and destroy these forces as well. Target designated Strike Lance Bravo.
I'm inbound to the LZ, Commander. Let's get moving to Tweak's position.
Shut yer trap. There were not 'hostile to all' forces.
Oh fer cryin out loud. There were no 'hostile to all' units.
I hate talking when it's not necessary.
You are not clear to speak this.
There's that mystery unit, Commander! Watch yourself. They're designated 'Draconis Delta'.
We have no information on what they might be packing, but we need to take them out before we get out of here.
Commander, a DEST dropship just landed more units on the field. They're designed 'Support Lance'.
Tweak must've pissed off the Combine quite a bit for them to send this much tonnage her way.
So much wasted space on unnecessary JSON.
Commander, we have a DEST dropship inbound. The drop zone is marked. Watch yourself.
Commander, there's an inbound dropship with that mystery insignia on it. Drop zone is marked. Watch yourself.
